window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Murmur and Fable are left reeling after Somnia’s servers crash, and nothing is quite the same. Even as they challenge new dungeons, Murmur is haunted by an old enemy who seeks to take her down a dark path.&nbsp;</p> <p>Meanwhile, Laria and Shayla struggle to hide Wren’s prolonged immersion in the game from coworkers and sponsors alike, forcing them to seek out unlikely allies.&nbsp;</p> <p>As more people are made aware of Wren’s predicament, freeing her from Somnia becomes even more crucial. However, it seems the game has other plans for her, and not even the AIs know what those are.</p>"; 
